'''Adolf Hitler''' ndi mtsogoleri wa dziko la [[Germany]] kuyambira 1934 mpaka 1945. Adolf anakhala mtsogoleri wa Nazi Party, ndipo anakhala  Chancellor wa Germany mu chaka cha 1933 ndiponso ''FÃ¼hrer (fyula)'' mu chaka cha 1934. Muzaka zomwe iye anali mtsogoleri, anayambitsa nkhondo yachiwiri yadziko lonse pamene ankhondo ake analowa mu dziko la Poland pa 1 seputembala mu chaka cha 1939. Iye anali akuyang'anila zonsezochitika munkhondoyi ndipo ndi amene anatsogolera kuti anthu achiyuda okwana 6 miliyoni aphedwe.

Hilter anadwila ku Austria - ndipo anakulira kumalo apafupi ndi Linz. Iye anapita ku Germany mu chaka cha 1913 ndipo analandila nyota pakuzipereka kwake kwa Germany mu nkhondo yoyamba yayikulu. Iye analowa chipani cha  

erman Workers' Party (DAP). Iye anasankhidwa kukhala mtsogoleri wa chipani cha Nazi mu chaka cha 1921. Mu chaka cha 1923, iye anayesela kulanda bomaku Munich koma analephera ndipo anamagidwa ndikupasidwa zaka zisanu mundende. Ali mundende iye analemba buku lake la moyo wake lotchedwa ''Mein Kampf'' (mazuzo anga). Akatulutsidwa mu ndende mu chaka cha 1924, Hilter  anapeza anthu omutsatila ambiri chifukwa chosagwirizana ndi versailles treaty, kukonda Germany ngati dziko, kudana ndi anthu achiyuda ndi chikomunisti ndi kuyankhula kwake kwa nthetenya. Iye anamayankhula zambiri zokhuza chikomunisti kuti  zinali zopangidwa ndi anthu achiyuda. 

Hilter anakhazikitsidwa kukhala mtsogoleri wa Germany ndipo anapatsidwa mphamvu zonse kulamulila Germany mu chaka cha 1933. Iye anali ndi ganizo lothamangitsa Ayuda onse mu Germany. Mu zaka zoyambiira za ulamuliro wake Hilter anabweretsa chitukuko zimene zinapangitsa anthu ambiri ku Germany kumutsatila. Iye analandanso madela amene kumakhala anrhu ena achi German mumayiko ogundizana nawo zomwe zinasangalatsa anthu ambiri. Iye anakhazikitsa ntchito yopanga zida za nkhondo. Ankhondo aku Germany analowa mu poland muchaka ch 1931 zimene zinapangitsa Britain ndi France kulowelera. Iye analamulanso ankhondo ake kulowa mu Soviet union. Kumapeto a chaka cha 1941, asilikali a Germany anali akalanda madela ambiri aku Ulaya komanso kumpoto kwa afrika. Koma zonsezi zina sintha mu chaka cha 1945 pamene asilikali a German anagonjetsedwa. pa 29 Apelo mu chaka cha 1945, Hilter anakwatila chibwenzi chake cha nthawi yayitali Eva Braun ku Berlin atangokhala masiku ochepa kuti adziphe. Mumasiku awiri atangokwatilana, Hilter ndi mkazi wake anadzipha kuwopa kugwidwa ndi ankhondo aku Soviet omwe anali atafika kale mu mzinda wa Berlin. Matupi awo anawotchedwa.

